Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  這不是旅行這只是留宿派對  對吧 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  很吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  千秋也醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們太吵了睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為好熱啊又不是旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  客人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以入睡的夜晚  由我提供鬼故事服務您意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以入睡的夜晚有冷氣的服務嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那種服務  客人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服務好差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼故事什麼的蠢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊睡覺吧  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你害怕了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩吧  鬼故事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐也參加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,講鬼故事來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼由內田開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  從我開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久很久以前在某個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是傳說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度的鬼故事就想嚇到我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.97,0:04:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個  該冬馬了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒的冰箱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡魔的洗衣機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖的吸塵器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用身邊的道具來引發恐懼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想增加點有趣的元素還特意讓我們三選一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選項只有家電啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼選吸塵器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸塵器嗎  選了吸塵器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  恐怖的吸塵器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  這是個什麼樣的故事來著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是虛張聲勢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有標題很厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  標題很可怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個故事我知道喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.51,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  不用勉強也可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  這回拜託你了  內田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:22.25,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看現在已經很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐～怖～的～吸～塵～器～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某對新婚夫婦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買了新家用的吸塵器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過在那個夜晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妻子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我新娘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新娘子喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事  我的新郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天買回來的吸塵器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼樣的吸塵器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天買回來的吸塵器？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:05:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了不會後悔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天買回來的吸塵器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是麩皮做成的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天買回來了個麩皮做的吸塵器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  麩皮的吸塵器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:29.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,360)\fad(0,500)}恐怖的吸塵器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:33.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注：「今日（きょう）お麩（ふ）の掃除機」发音\N与「恐怖（きょうふ）の掃除機」类似
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:33.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,360)\fad(500,0)}今天、麩皮的吸塵器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖的吸塵器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是冷笑話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個故事和恐怖的味噌汁相似啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  麩皮的味噌汁的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼故事怎麼辦啊  鬼故事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  到底是什麼樣的故事來著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得是收到了吸塵器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個故事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得是吸塵器裏發出了呻吟聲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把結局說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不應該有更厲害的結局麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對  呻吟聲就是結局了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登場的不是老夫老妻麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家各執一詞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呻吟聲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從哪發出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,講鬼怪故事就會招來鬼怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說吸塵器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:35.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要嚇我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是夢啊  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是春香的呻吟聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了什麼可怕的夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是個非常可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼很沉的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說鬼故事了  各自爆料自己喜歡的男性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼從誰開始講？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼按年齡大小來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南…南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都已經下半學期了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種高溫到底要持續到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的秋老虎真久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.94,0:08:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早～上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是新學期沒有精神啊  精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼熱你也這麼精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上就試著用左手吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右腳鞋子反著穿等等分散了注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算把炎熱忘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉了的炎熱一下子就把我擊倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要負責讓我涼快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  放學回家給你買冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  不能這樣慣她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中獎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天中獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免費讓你變得涼快不是挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊  好像長了蛀牙不能吃冰淇淋了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我蛀牙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給圭子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去交換有點難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在在控制甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子有點不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有個了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.67,0:10:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個中獎棒怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是還給夏奈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  好像很精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼痛和炎熱已經忘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得中的獎  還是還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊  好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治好蛀牙前先收著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日的茂草  武士們留下的夢的點滴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:38.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}元俳句出自松尾芭蕉「夏草や 兵どもが 夢の跡」\N比喻功名利禄只在旦夕之间转瞬即逝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  別抄襲別人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就知道是我中到的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:52.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}夏日的茂草  強者們留下的夢的點滴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙  到底抄襲了幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  這個是去年中到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獎小到收起來後就會忘掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈給的禮物？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.33,0:11:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去看牙醫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}南家鬥惡龍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:17.93,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}沙漠裏倒下  篇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}南家鬥惡龍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:22.92,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}綠洲發現？！篇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行啊  三宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健叔  在喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸說  酒在夏天會很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過據說很苦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦中有美味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田  酒要20歲以後才能喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:11:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:12:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  這個給健叔拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是毛豆啊  也有我的份嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有我也會自己偷拿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼打我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷吃毛豆是這麼重的罪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…因為有蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚊子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  這不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  是蚊子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干…幹什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擅自吃了我的冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便吃妹妹的冰淇淋有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是把中獎棒給你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得60日元的棒冰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和含稅共計284日元的高級冰激凌相提並論嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許再使用暴力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有蚊子  一隻大蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就先這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  是蚊子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宮同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健叔是放假了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說是帶薪休假哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是帶薪休假？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:12.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是休假  但也能拿到工資哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸說的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有工資
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說現在健是既有錢拿又有休假咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是贏家嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我先去給健叔揉揉肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前南家住宿旅行的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的長篇故事害得我睡眠不足
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎麼補償我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得大家都互相說著話然後就睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說啊  要是把斑馬的斑馬線去掉應該就變成馬了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是斑馬是白的  所以會變成白馬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  你的故事會很長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我困了就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你困了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:13:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不困
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是條紋的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我把這段講完了再去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事很長的是夏奈吧  我可是很困的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:18.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛打我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一隻帶條紋的蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  下雨的時候你對我潑水了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說之前梅雨的時候嗎  虧你還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有一隻眼神很兇的蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了冬馬  有蚊子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒有  吉野身上沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂等一下  我到底是為了什麼被打
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…總覺得有蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫總覺得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有蚊子！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有蚊子！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有蚊子！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有什麼蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有  就是有蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是想打我吧  老實承認吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承認了的話還能打你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健被壓扁了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有一隻又大又帶條紋眼神很兇的蚊子…在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  健叔已經睡著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被蚊子叮了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿健沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能變成這樣的大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都訂好餐廳了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  這傢伙放假了還來我們家就說明…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天還是對他好點吧  就今天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然已經不早了  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好夏奈  打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健那傢伙  今天也沒事幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也給他上茶了  也算招待過他了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就隨便對付下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣老是來還真煩人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都聽得見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來春香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去買東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的早飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那午飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要餓死我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己做點什麼不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經快餓到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  健你之前吃了春香做的類似毛豆的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著我的眼睛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的侄女正餓著肚子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為叔叔你不覺得自己應該做點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是叔叔  是表哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的侄女啊  就只想吃一點點好吃的午餐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛背過身去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.87,0:17:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的侄女作為一個日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到有東西在轉就想吃一種食物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:17:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦千秋  你指的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在轉的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  沒想到會請我們吃壽司
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  有錢人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不巧的時候碰上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是正巧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  有錢人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉有錢人  人變多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,0:18:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  雖說是沒關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過人均1000日元哦  要遵守啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這間店有從每碟100日元至500日元
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.29,0:18:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共分5個等級
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純白碟  100日元
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好看的帶鑲邊的碟子  200日元
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來有那麼點高檔的碟子  300日元
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頗有厚重感的碟子  400日元
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後是看起來很豪華的碟子  500日元
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說有一千日元就能吃的很飽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一不小心就會超過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.23,0:19:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的解說  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  請給我兩碟金槍魚大肥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真厲害  上來就點兩碟500日元的結束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要蛋卷  蒸蛋  鮭魚子  還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是蛋呢  反正你就是各種蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才吃的那個叫不出名字的白色食物  好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈牙的  脆脆的  一瞬間就化了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白身魚的壽司有很多種呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟是吃了哪一種呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  我用魷魚和你的甜蝦交換著吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在是100  200  300日元的各一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共計300日元對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦千秋  計算有問題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不應該是很聰明的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  我的甜蝦和你的扇貝交換下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是兩碟100  一碟200  兩碟300
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了這麼多還只花了500日元啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  千秋再算一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田  我用扇貝和你的鮭魚子交換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野  我用鮭魚子和你最後的金槍魚大肥交換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  終於換到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共7000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去之前讓我再想一想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是一個人1000
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最後卻花了7000
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.69,0:20:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7000？六個人應該是6000吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  千秋的碟子有點不對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後有連續兩碟500的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光那兩碟就1000了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不守規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是不是少算了一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是藤岡的份！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看它嘴邊粘著飯粒就是證據
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:20:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  正好碰到真希和淳子所以說了一會話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服哦  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋真乖啊  我現在就去做午飯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.31,0:21:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經吃過壽司當午飯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.93,0:21:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壽司？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健帶我們去的  春香也一起來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說春香姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去買午飯的材料…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  我們去吃壽司吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
